snippet: The Phoenix police have made two arrests in the September beating death of Alexis Urbina, a 17-year-old national champion boxer.
abstract: Phoenix police arrest Robert Chavez and Joseph Corrales on charges of murder and related crimes in September beating death of Alexis Urbina, national champion boxer.
lead_paragraph: The Phoenix police have made two arrests in the September beating death of Alexis Urbina, a 17-year-old national champion boxer.

headline.main: Arrests Made in Death of Teenage Boxer
